name: Sfera Ebbasta - FanGame
description:
We decided to celebrate the outstanding success of Sfera’s new album, “Famoso”, which is breaking every record all over the world, with a little game inspired by his unstoppable rise.

Avoid obstacles and haters in this run to success!

Share the score with your friends.

Developed by Oltre - Made to Imagine
